'''尤里·斯特茨'''（{{lang-uk|Юрій Ярославович Стець}}；{{bd|1975年|12月29日}}）是[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]的一位記者和政治人物<ref name="DV">{{cite web | url=http://dovidka.com.ua/user/?code=171208 | title=Стець Юрій Ярославович (Yuriy Yaroslavovych Stets) | work=Dovidka | date=4 December 2014 | accessdate=4 December 2014 | language=uk | archive-date=2015-12-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210211847/http://dovidka.com.ua/user/?code=171208 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。他在第二次[[阿爾謝尼·亞采尼克|阿爾謝尼·亞采尼克]]內閣中擔任訊息政策部部長<ref name="KP4DEC">{{cite news | url=http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv-post-plus/journalists-media-rights-activists-demand-abolishing-of-newly-formed-ministry-of-truth-374003.html | title=Journalists, free speech activists demand abolishing of newly-formed 'Ministry of Truth' | work=Kyiv Post | date=4 December 2014 | accessdate=4 December 2014 | archive-date=2015-12-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210211949/http://www.kyivpost.com/content/kyiv-post-plus/journalists-media-rights-activists-demand-abolishing-of-newly-formed-ministry-of-truth-374003.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年12月8日，他辭去了部長職務，因為他覺得他已經「達到了目標」<ref name=ysr81215>[http://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/309925.html Ukraine's minister of information policy resigns] {{Wayback|url=http://en.interfax.com.ua/news/general/309925.html |date=20160113185351 }}, [[Interfax_Ukraine|Interfax Ukraine]] (8 December 2015)</ref>。他是[[彼得·波羅申科集團|彼得·波羅申科集團]]的一員。

